{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852271089,"sessionID":"ses_286f4eed9ffe5xOXE2nxjMMXP7","part":{"id":"prt_d790b2a16001N0BJZjXvIpen9w","messageID":"msg_d790b1ef2001jMsQqW3VUAJEcb","sessionID":"ses_286f4eed9ffe5xOXE2nxjMMXP7","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_d607a528b8de4ad5abd578ee","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/store  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Core Implementation Verification\n11: \n12: - [ ] **1.1** Verify `valkeyStore` struct defined in `pkg/store/store_valkey.go` with fields: `cli`, `sessionPrefix`, `expiryIndexKey`, `lastActivityIndexKey`\n13: - [ ] **1.2** Verify constants are accessible: `sessionKeyPrefix`, `sessionExpiryIndexKey`, `sessionLastActivityKey` (currently shared from `store_redis.go`)\n14: - [ ] **1.3** Verify `makeValkeyOptions()` parses environment variables: `VALKEY_ADDR`, `VALKEY_PASSWORD`, `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED`, `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE`, `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE`\n15: - [ ] **1.4** Verify `VALKEY_ADDR` is required — returns error if empty\n16: - [ ] **1.5** Verify `VALKEY_PASSWORD` is required when `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is not \"false\"\n17: - [ ] **1.6** Verify `go build ./pkg/store/...` compiles successfully\n18: \n19: ---\n20: \n21: ## Phase 2: Basic Operations\n22: \n23: - [ ] **2.1** Verify `newValkeyStore()` creates client and performs PING check\n24: - [ ] **2.2** Verify `Ping(ctx)` executes `cli.B().Ping().Build()` and uses `cli.Do(ctx, result)`\n25: - [ ] **2.3** Verify `Ping` returns error on disconnected server\n26: - [ ] **2.4** Verify `GetSandboxBySessionID` uses GET command and returns `ErrNotFound` when key not exists\n27: - [ ] **2.5** Verify `GetSandboxBySessionID` handles `valkey.IsValkeyNil(resp.Error())` correctly\n28: - [ ] **2.6** Verify `Close()` calls `cli.Close()` and returns any error\n29: \n30: ---\n31: \n32: ## Phase 3: StoreSandbox Atomicity\n33: \n34: - [ ] **3.1** Verify `StoreSandbox` uses `DoMulti` with: SETNX (session key), ZADD (expiry index), ZADD (last_activity index)\n35: - [ ] **3.2** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates nil sandbox — returns error \"sandbox is nil\"\n36: - [ ] **3.3** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates zero ExpiresAt — returns error \"invalid expiry: ExpiresAt is zero\"\n37: - [ ] **3.4** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates empty SessionID — returns error \"session ID is required\"\n38: - [ ] **3.5** Verify ZSET scores: expiry uses `ExpiresAt.Unix()`, last activity uses `time.Now().Unix()`\n39: \n40: ---\n41: \n42: ## Phase 4: UpdateSandbox\n43: \n44: - [ ] **4.1** Verify `UpdateSandbox` uses SET with XX flag (not SetNX)\n45: - [ ] **4.2** Verify `UpdateSandbox` fails with error \"key not exists\" when key does not exist\n46: - [ ] **4.3** Verify `UpdateSandbox` does NOT modify expiry or last-activity ZSETs\n47: - [ ] **4.4** Verify error handling for `valkey.IsValkeyNil(resp.Error())` case\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## Phase 5: DeleteSandbox\n52: \n53: - [ ] **5.1** Verify `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` uses DoMulti with DEL and ZREM (both indices)\n54: - [ ] **5.2** Verify deletion succeeds for non-existent session (no error returned)\n55: \n56: ---\n57: \n58: ## Phase 6: List Operations\n59: \n60: - [ ] **6.1** Verify `ListExpiredSandboxes` uses ZRANGEBYSCORE on expiry index\n61: - [ ] **6.2** Verify `ListInactiveSandboxes` uses ZRANGEBYSCORE on last_activity index\n62: - [ ] **6.3** Verify both list operations return `nil, nil` when limit <= 0\n63: - [ ] **6.4** Verify list operations use MGET to load JSON for each session ID\n64: - [ ] **6.5** Verify orphan ZSET members are skipped gracefully (check for `item.IsNil()`)\n65: \n66: ---\n67: \n68: ## Phase 7: UpdateSessionLastActivity\n69: \n70: - [ ] **7.1** Verify `UpdateSessionLastActivity` verifies key existence first via EXISTS\n71: - [ ] **7.2** Verify returns `ErrNotFound` when session key does not exist\n72: - [ ] **7.3** Verify uses `time.Now()` when timestamp is zero\n73: - [ ] **7.4** Verify rejects empty session ID with error \"session ID is required\"\n74: - [ ] **7.5** Verify ZADD uses provided timestamp as score\n75: \n76: ---\n77: \n78: ## Phase 8: Unit Tests\n79: \n80: - [ ] **8.1** Create `pkg/store/store_valkey_test.go` — unit tests with mock Valkey\n81: - [ ] **8.2** Verify `go test ./pkg/store/... -v` passes\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ## Dependencies\n86: \n87: - `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go`\n88: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types`\n89: \n90: ---\n91: \n92: ## References\n93: \n94: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-014/delta-spec.md` (if exists)\n95: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md` (Store interface)\n96: - Design: `session-store/design.md`\n97: - Spec: `session-store/spec.md`\n98: - Redis implementation: `changes/AR-013/tasks.md` (for comparison)\n\n(End of file - total 98 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/store  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core Implementation Verification\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Verify `valkeyStore` struct defined in `pkg/store/store_valkey.go` with fields: `cli`, `sessionPrefix`, `expiryIndexKey`, `lastActivityIndexKey`\n- [ ] **1.2** Verify constants are accessible: `sessionKeyPrefix`, `sessionExpiryIndexKey`, `sessionLastActivityKey` (currently shared from `store_redis.go`)\n- [ ] **1.3** Verify `makeValkeyOptions()` parses environment variables: `VALKEY_ADDR`, `VALKEY_PASSWORD`, `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED`, `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE`, `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE`\n- [ ] **1.4** Verify `VALKEY_ADDR` is required — returns error if empty\n- [ ] **1.5** Verify `VALKEY_PASSWORD` is required when `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is not \"false\"\n- [ ] **1.6** Verify `go build ./pkg/store/...` compiles successfully\n\n---\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775852271067,"end":1775852271087}}}}
